        "info": {
          "title": "line_sketch_generation",
          "version": "qoo5wjrelgknluan",
          "description": "# Sketch (linear mode) Generation\n\n![alt text](image.png) ![alt text](image-1.png)\nThis project contains pipeline for sketches generation based on loaded image:\n• lineart\n• sketches\nFor tuning and managing of result, you should manage following settings:\n\n- target text-prompt;\n- negative text-prompt;\n- num of steps;\n- random seed;\n- target image size;\n\n## Project structure\n\n```\n|- diffusers_helper -- generation part of pipeline (sketches in general)\n|- lineart_models -- tools for linear processing\n|- processor.py -- modelu with main funcs for image and promp processing\n|- gradio_app.py -- script for running gradio app for sketches and lines contours generation []\n|- service.py -- BentoML service class for serving of ml model\n|- requests_example.py -- Example of request for BentoML service\n```\n\n## How to run\n\n1. clone repo\n2. `cd line_sketch_generation`\n3. create venv and install `requirements.txt`\n4. run service with bentoml or gradio\n\n    4.1. for running **gradio mode**: `python gradio_app.py` and open localhost:8000 in a browser\n\n    4.2. for running **bento service mode**: `bentoml serve` (see request example in `requests_example.py`)\n\n5. just use it\n\n! Note: promts and other setting are locked for bentoservice mode (see properties of SketchGenerator class)\n! current version supported only CPU\n\n\n## How to containerize\n\n### By Bentoml \n\n1. clone repo\n2. `cd line_sketch_generation`\n3. create venv and install `requirements.txt`\n\nFOR CPU\n4.  `bentoml build`\n5. copy tag and run\n6. `bentoml containerize \u003ctag\u003e`\nFor running use `docker run --rm -p 3000:3000 \u003ctag\u003e`\n\n\nFOR GPU\n4.  `bentoml build -f bentofile_gpu.yaml`\n5. copy tag and run\n6. `bentoml containerize \u003ctag\u003e`\nFor running use `docker run  --gpus all --rm -p 3000:3000 \u003ctag\u003e`\n\n\nSee request example in `requests_example.py`\n\n### By vanila Docker\n1. clone repo\n2. `cd line_sketch_generation`\n3. ` docker build . -t bentolinear`\n4. `docker run -ti --rm -p 3000:3000 bentolinear:latest`\n\n\n---\n\n## Core model information\n\n* **link**: \u003chttps://huggingface.co/spaces/KBlueLeaf/Sketch-Gen/tree/main\u003e\n* **title**: Sketch Gen\n* **sdk**: gradio (gradio_app)\n* **sdk_version**: 4.37.2\n* **app_file**: gradio_app.py\n* **pinned**: false\n* **license:** apache-2.0\n\nCheck out the configuration reference at \u003chttps://huggingface.co/docs/hub/spaces-config-reference\u003e\n",
          "contact": {
            "name": "BentoML Team",
            "email": "contact@bentoml.com"
          }
        },
